parameters:
If you talk to Ruin and choose "Yes" → you'll battle Gargan,
and then it's on to the ending.

If you battle Gargan and lose, you'll return to before the
battle. If you win, you'll proceed to the ending.
ルイン立ち絵　通常
\n<Ruin>Anyway, you're here to tell me to go to Marion, right?

\n<Ruin>...You're so transparent. You're nothing like the original
modified girl.
\n<Eury>Dr. Marion wants to help you. There's no mistake about it!

\n<Ruin>The Monster Core I created has been destroyed. There's
nothing more I can do on the side of the monsters.

\n<Ruin>It was a foolish act that started from a petty sense of
inferiority. Truly, truly foolish...
ルイン立ち絵　通常

\n<???>Oh my, it seems like the conversation is moving along
without me.
ルイン立ち絵 驚き

\n<???>Ruin. You hated Marion because everything was going well for
her.

\n<???>You're the one who destroyed the new model Sexaroid in
transit and framed Eury, weren't you?

\n<???>Even if you try to return to being human now, it's already
too late.

\n<???>Besides, that promise you made with me will now be null and
void.
ルイン立ち絵 驚き
\n<Eury>Wait a minute! Who are you exactly!?
\n<Eury>I won't let you lay a hand on Ruin-san!

\n<Gargan>I've crawled up from the depths of hell because I want a
rematch with Makina!!
\n<Eury>I won't let you! I will defeat you right here!
\n<Gargan>I'll kill you quickly and then go fight Makina!!!

\n<Eury>I can't let a dangerous being like you roam free in the
city!
ルイン立ち絵 驚き
\n<Ruin>I'll assist you, so somehow defeat that guy...!!!

LL_InfoPopupWIndowMV showWindow 入手：\i[87]\C[14]２週間以内クリアの証\C[0] 120 auto auto 0
\n<Gargan>I can't fall to hell until I fight Makina!!!
ルイン立ち絵 驚き
\n<Ruin>Don't deliver the final blow, we need him for...!!!
\n<Eury>(Such a pity, we were so close...!)
ルイン立ち絵 驚き
\n<Marion>Makina, hurry up and kill that bastard!
\n<Makina>As you wish, I'll be the one to bury you.
\n<Gargan>How about we fight when we're both in the best condition?
\n<Makina>...Just don't come back to life again.
\n<Marion>You dumbass moron! That's not what I mean.

\n<Marion>There's a ton of things I want to ask. For starters, come to
the base.
